{"id":826239686,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"3 months, 4 weeks","timestamp":1666221170,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"82 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/826239686/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"11.8 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n\n    int lengthOfLongestSubstring(string str) {\n    int n = str.size();\n    int res = 0; // result\n \n    for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {\n         \n        // Note : Default values in visited are false\n        vector<bool> visited(256);  \n \n        for (int j = i; j < n; j++) {\n \n            // If current character is visited\n            // Break the loop\n            if (visited[str[j]] == true)\n                break;\n \n            // Else update the result if\n            // this window is larger, and mark\n            // current character as visited.\n            else {\n                res = max(res, j - i + 1);\n                visited[str[j]] = true;\n            }\n        }\n \n        // Remove the first character of previous\n        // window\n        visited[str[i]] = false;\n    }\n    return res;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters","has_notes":false}
